Does that answer recognize me?

Absolutely! Hamsters can recognize their owners by scent and sound. The more time you spend gently handling and talking to them, the more familiar and comfortable they become with you. They might not show it the same way as cats or dogs, but they definitely know who their favorite human is!
How do I know if my hamster fucks with me or not?

You can tell your hamster is comfortable with you if it approaches you without hesitation, takes treats from your hand, or allows gentle handling. If it seems relaxed, grooms itself around you, or even climbs onto your hand, those are great signs. If it’s hiding or acting stressed, it might need more time to get used to you.
